{"type":"message","id":"0a88c8b0","parentId":"47aa645d","timestamp":"2026-03-02T01:40:07.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"工作空间的 Git 没有远程配置，F 盘有 xiaoxia 目录但还没配置 GitHub 备份。老板问这个问题可能是想确认是否有 GitHub 备份，或者想让我配置。我需要如实汇报当前状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"老板，目前 **GitHub 备份位置尚未配置**：\n\n### 当前 Git 状态\n\n| 位置 | Git 状态 | 远程仓库 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| `C:\\Users\\14015\\.openclaw\\workspace` | ✓ 有 .git | ❌ **无远程配置** |\n| `G:\\openClaw\\xiaoxia` | ✓ 有 .git | ✅ `https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw.git` |\n\n---\n\n### F 盘输出目录\n\n```\nF:\\2025ideazdjx\\openClaw-project\\\n├── daxia/    (大虾 - WSL2)\n└── xiaoxia/  (小虾 - Windows) ← 刚创建，未初始化 Git\n```\n\n---\n\n### 需要配置吗？\n\n如果您有 GitHub 仓库用于备份小虾的配置和记忆，我可以：\n\n1. **初始化工作空间 Git 远程**\n   ```bash\n   git remote add origin <your-repo-url>\n   ```\n\n2. **初始化 F 盘输出目录 Git**\n   ```bash\n   cd F:\\2025ideazdjx\\openClaw-project\\xiaoxia\n   git init\n   git remote add origin <your-repo-url>\n   ```\n\n3. **更新备份脚本** - 增加 Git 推送步骤\n\n---\n\n老板，您的 GitHub 备份仓库地址是？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":35036,"output":421,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35457,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772415590315}}
